1.	Visual Studio Code 
(IDE, which enables programmers to consolidate the different aspects of writing a computer program.)
https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/languages/javascript
Recommended Extension for Javascript: 
•	GitLen, 
•	Code Spell Checker, 
•	Debugger for Chrome, 
•	Prettier (Uncheck the auto semicolon option)
 
1.	Javascript - ES6 
(e.g. Arrow Function, Function Rest Parameter, Array.map() )
JavaScript ES6 (EcmaScript 2015)
 
1.	React.JS 
Focus on Functional Component
Stage 1 - Idea of React:(State and Props) 
https://zh-hant.reactjs.org/tutorial/tutorial.html
Stage 2 - React Documentation:(Life Cycle, Hooks, JSX)
https://zh-hant.reactjs.org/docs/getting-started.html
 
1.	Gatsby JS (Static Site Generator)
https://www.gatsbyjs.com/docs/tutorial/
https://www.gatsbyjs.com/docs/how-to/
 
1.	Ant Design (React UI library)
https://ant.design/docs/react/getting-started
 
1.	Less.js (language extension for CSS)
https://lesscss.org/
 
1.	Netifly (serverless platform to build and deploy, on web apps)
https://www.gatsbyjs.com/docs/how-to/previews-deploys-hosting/deploying-to-netlify/
 

 
 
1.	Git Commit 格式:
 
Type -  <描述/>
 
Feat: 新加/修改功能
 
Remove: 移除功能/組件
 
Style: 改善Layout (Css, 串字, layout 的變動)
 
Perf: 改善代碼質素
 
Fix: 除錯
 
Refactor: 文件結構上的改變
 
Ignore: 可以忽視
 
例子:  Feat - 新增服務頁面

